name: Superfone
description:
Superfone provides a business mobile number that can be shared by your entire team. Use 1 single shared number with your staff to make calls in parallel & manage Whatsapp messages! We also offer a CRM & lead management platform and other capabilities.

Only Rs. 700/month for 1 number with 3 staff members that supports concurrent calls & Whatsapp API capabilities!! See our website for updated price details
focus_areas: Shared inbox, Small-medium business, Single shared number for calls and Whatsapp, Integrated & all in one solution
